CatDescriptText: Related image published in advertisement in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 1, 1960, pg. 20, with text reading: "The World Series Crowds Will Head for The 600 Bar - If You Didn't Get a Ticket...See the Game Here on TV - The 600 Bar, 600 Ann Street, Homestead - 'The Crossroads where Good Friends meet.'"
TitMainTitle: Man, possibly bartender, and woman, posed behind bar with lobster and sailboat patterned awning, ship's wheel, and Budweiser sign, in 600 Bar, Homestead, another version
